<title>RFQ报价 — Mukul Gautam / 女婴套装</title>
<style>
  * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
  body { font-family: "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", sans-serif; background:#f2f3f5; color:#1d2129; padding:20px; }
