<body>
<div class="container">

<h1>RFQ 报价表单</h1>
<p class="subtitle">客户：Mukul Gautam（印度） | 仅剩 <span style="color:#f53f3f;font-weight:700;">1</span> 个报价席位</p>

<!-- 买家信息 -->
<div class="card">
  <div class="buyer-card">
    <div class="buyer-avatar">M</div>
    <div class="buyer-info">
      <div class="buyer-name">Mukul Gautam <span style="font-size:12px;color:#86909c;font-weight:400;">· India</span></div>
      <div class="buyer-tags">
        <span class="tag gold">历史订单额高</span>
        <span class="tag">邮件认证</span>
        <span class="tag">RFQ有成交</span>
        <span class="tag">高效回复</span>
        <span class="tag warn">已报9家 | 仅剩1席</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- 深度分析 -->
<div class="card">
  <div class="section-title">深度分析</div>
  <div class="analysis">
    <p><strong>需求拆解：</strong>买家原话问的是"fabric composition details for 0-3M pink"，说明他在做产品筛选对比，不是随便发。他之前联系了Kyle Gong没回复，我们是替补进场。聚酯纤维（Polyester）标在标题中，但详情里又写了Denim（牛仔布）——存在矛盾，报价中以Polyester为准回复，引导买家澄清确认。</p>
    <p style="margin-top:8px;"><strong>竞争态势：</strong>已有9家报价，我们最后1席。差异化靠<strong>工厂硬实力</strong>：BSCI/ISO9001认证 + 帮宝适/迪士尼代工背书 + 自有打样能力 + 可配合找面料。</p>
    <p style="margin-top:8px;"><strong>策略：</strong>买家目前处于比较阶段，"能打样、能找面料"比报低价更重要。报价中突出打样路径和定制能力，引导下一步。</p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- 产品及价格 -->
<div class="card">
  <div class="section-title"><span class="num">一、</span>产品及价格 1</div>

  <div class="field">
    <div class="label"><span class="required">*</span>产品名称</div>
    <div class="value">2026 Summer Baby Girl Ruffled Short-Sleeve Romper with Floral Bow and Layered Skirt Set (2pcs) — 0-3 Months, Pink, Polyester</div>
  </div>

  <div class="field">
    <div class="label">产品编号</div>
    <div class="value">XS-BG-SS26-001</div>
  </div>

  <div class="field">
    <div class="label"><span class="required">*</span>产品细节</div>
    <div class="value">Material: 100% Polyester, lightweight and breathable for summer.<br>
Size: 0-3 Months (approx. 52-59cm height).<br>
Design: Pullover romper with ruffled short sleeves, floral bow decoration, layered skirt bottom. 2-piece set (romper + skirt).<br>
Printing: Heat-transfer floral pattern.<br>
Closure: Pullover style, snap buttons at crotch for easy diaper change.<br>
Craftsmanship: Flatlock seams (5-thread) for baby comfort, no skin irritation. All fabric pre-washed for softness.<br>
Customization: Full OEM/ODM supported — custom fabric, color, print, size range, label, and packaging.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="field">
    <div class="label">产品图片/文件 <span class="file-hint">（最多5个附件，≤5MB，支持 jpg/png/pdf/doc/xlsx）</span></div>
    <div class="upload-suggest">
      <div class="tit">建议上传（见下方详细清单）</div>
      <li>类似女婴套装产品实拍图 2-3张</li>
      <li>工厂简介/资质一览（PDF 1页）</li>
      <li>BSCI / ISO9001 证书</li>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="border-top:1px solid #f2f3f5; margin:14px 0; padding-top:14px;">
    <div class="section-title" style="border-bottom:none; margin-bottom:10px;">价格详情</div>

    <div class="row3">
      <div class="field"><div class="label"><span class="required">*</span>装运条款</div><div class="value">FOB</div></div>
      <div class="field"><div class="label"><span class="required">*</span>港口</div><div class="value">Guangzhou</div></div>
      <div class="field"><div class="label"><span class="required">*</span>报价有效期</div><div class="value">2026-06-18</div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="row3">
      <div class="field"><div class="label"><span class="required">*</span>货币单位</div><div class="value">USD</div></div>
      <div class="field"><div class="label"><span class="required">*</span>数量单位</div><div class="value">Pieces</div></div>
      <div class="field"><div class="label"><span class="required">*</span>付款方式</div><div class="value">T/T (40% deposit, 60% before shipment)</div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="row2">
      <div class="field"><div class="label"><span class="required">*</span>订购数量</div><div class="value">500 — 10,000 Pieces</div></div>
      <div class="field"><div class="label"><span class="required">*</span>产品单价</div><div class="value price">【待老板审核后填入】 USD / Piece</div></div>
    </div>

    <div style="font-size:11px; color:#86909c; margin-top:6px;">区间价格：1-499pcs（样品价）| 500-2999pcs | 3000-9999pcs | 10000+pcs — 待老板审核</div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- 报价补充信息 -->
<div class="card">
  <div class="section-title"><span class="num">二、</span>报价补充信息</div>

  <div class="field">
    <div class="label">提供样品</div>
    <div class="radio-group">
      <span class="radio active">是</span>
      <span class="radio">否</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="field">
    <div class="label">提供免费样品</div>
    <div class="radio-group">
      <span class="radio">是</span>
      <span class="radio active">否（收费）</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="field">
    <div class="label">样品运费支付方</div>
    <div class="radio-group">
      <span class="radio active">买家</span>
      <span class="radio">卖家</span>
      <span class="radio">协商</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="field">
    <div class="label">预计的寄样日期</div>
    <div class="value">确认后 7-10 天</div>
  </div>

  <div class="field">
    <div class="label">样品费说明</div>
    <div class="value">样品费全额收取。大货订单确认后，样品费可从大货总金额中<strong>全额抵扣</strong>。</div>
  </div>

  <div class="field">
    <div class="label"><span class="required">*</span>给买家的消息</div>
    <div class="value" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">Hi Mukul,

Thank you for your RFQ! I understand you reached out to Kyle earlier — apologies for the delayed response, I'm following up from our team.

Regarding your question about fabric composition for the 0-3M pink baby girl outfit:

The shell fabric is 100% Polyester — lightweight, quick-drying, and soft against baby skin, ideal for summer wear. We use pre-washed polyester to ensure no skin irritation for newborns. The ruffled sleeves and layered skirt are triple-stitched for durability, and the crotch area features snap buttons for easy diaper changes.

About us — Yiyang Xiaoxingxing Garments:
🏭 6,000+ sqm factory with 200+ workers (est. 2015)
✅ BSCI & ISO9001 certified
🏅 OEM partner for Pampers (2024 Olympic edition), Disney, Johnson's, Unicharm
🧪 In-house 5A/7A antibacterial treatment facility
✂️ Full customization: fabric, print, size, label, packaging

Sample & Order Info:
• Sample: Available, 7-10 days after order confirmation. Sample fee charged but <strong>fully deductible</strong> from bulk order.
• Sample shipping: Buyer covers courier cost.
• MOQ for bulk: 500 pcs/style/color/size.
• Payment: T/T 40% deposit, 60% before shipment.

We don't stock ready pink polyester for this exact item, but we work with a wide supplier network and can source the right fabric quickly. If you have a specific fabric swatch or Pantone color reference, we can match it precisely.

Happy to send you photos of similar baby girl sets we've produced. What's the best way to share more details with you — email or WhatsApp?

Best regards,
[Your Name]
Yiyang Xiaoxingxing Garments Co., Ltd.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="field">
    <div class="label">文件上传 <span class="file-hint">（最多6个附件，≤5MB）</span></div>
    <div class="upload-suggest">
      <div class="tit">建议上传以下文件</div>
      <li><strong>1. 工厂简介 PDF</strong> — 1页，含工厂大门/车间/样品间照片、核心数据（6000㎡/200+人/2015年成立）、认证标识（BSCI/ISO9001）、品牌合作logo墙（Pampers/Disney/Johnson's/Unicharm）</li>
      <li><strong>2. 类似产品实拍图 2-3张</strong> — 已生产过的女婴套装/连衣裙，展示做工细节（平缝/暗扣/印花清晰度）</li>
      <li><strong>3. BSCI 或 ISO9001 证书截图</strong> — 增强信任</li>
      <li><strong>4. 面料色卡/样本册照片（如有）</strong> — 展示粉色涤纶面料选项</li>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

